#

Cheese and Apple Toast

15 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

BreakfastSnack

Tags:

QuickEasySnackBreakfast

Description

A quick and delicious toast topped with creamy cheese and sweet apple slices, perfect for breakfast or a snack!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • cream cheese (or brie): 4 tablespoons
  • apple (sliced thinly): 1 medium
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon (optional): 1 teaspoon
